<h2>Welcome to fractalcomposer.com!</h2>

<h3><a href="http://fractalcomposer.com">fractalcomposer.com</a> lets you compose interesting music using the self-similar nature of fractals to generate an entire piece of music.  You simply need to give it a short melody that defines the fractal shape.</h3>

<h3>Not sure what any of that means?  Visit the <a href="/about">about</a> page to learn more or go to the <a href="/examples">examples</a> page to see some of the results.</h3>

<h3>Or head straight to the <a href="/compose">compose</a> page to create your own piece of fractal music!</h3>
